content: Xander's AI is now better at predicting market trends with an ethical lens. Emily and I had a blast exploring an old subway station, captured some incredible moments for our blog. Also, got an email from a college, they want me to speak on ethical AI in finance.

Xander's ethical trading module is now fully integrated, and it's showing promising results. Emily and I are planning our next urban exploration trip, this time to an abandoned amusement park. Got some thoughts on AI and personal growth to share at the conference.

Xander's AI now has a social impact score feature, making trading decisions even more ethical. Emily and I are preparing for our Catskills getaway, feeling the need to unplug and reflect. Also, got another gig to consult on ethical AI, feels like my career is really taking shape.
